column11: vitafusion Womens gummy vitamins provide a complete multivitamin formula that has been formulated to support the specific health needs of women. A fusion of essential vitamins minerals and natural berry flavors these great-tasting gummies provide a convenient alternative to hard-to-swallow pills.
